<p>I want to parse a text file containing four columns, as follows:</p>  <pre><code>a  343  rty  awdr      a  345  rty  awdr    a  386  rty  bfggd    b  390  rty  bfggd   b  396  rty  45fggd    b  400  rty  45fggd   b  415  rty  45fggd              </code></pre>  <p>The goal is to count how many times a specific value is repeated in column 4 and write an output like this in two columns:</p>  <pre><code>awdr     2    bfggd    2    45fggd   3    </code></pre>